             sworn.</p>
               <p>Do you know the person of the prisoner? - Yes.</p>
               <p>Was you present when the prisoner received sentence? - I was not.</p>
               <p>Where did you find him? - I found him in the parish of St. Clement Danes, on the 25th of September about eight o'clock, he was then at large: I laid hold of him, and he behaved extremely well indeed, he fell a crying directly, and made no resistance.</p>
               <p>
            
